Clio Goldsmith https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clio_Goldsmith 0 Clio Goldsmith (born 16 June 1957) is a French former actress, appearing mostly as a Femme fatale in some films of the early 1980s. She is a member of the prominent Goldsmith family through her father ecologist Edward Goldsmith.
